Sent Tuesday September AM Subject Fw AOL Original Message Lets hope it works if it doesntno loss To all of my friends I do not usually forward messages but this is from my good friend Pearlas Sanborn and she really is an attorneyIf she says that this will work it WILL work After allwhat have you got to lose SORRY EVERYBODYJUST HAD TO TAKE THE CHANCE Im an attorney and I know the law This thing is for real Rest assured AOL and Intel will follow through with their promises for fear of facing multimillion dollar class action suit similar to the one filed by Pepsico against General Electric not too long ago Were not going to help them out with their email beta test without getting a little something for our time My brothers girlfriend got in on this a few months ago When I went to visit him for the BaylorUT gameshe showed me her check It was for the sum of and was stamped Paid In Full Like I said before I know the law and this is for real If you dont believe me you can email her at Shes eager to answer any questions you guys might have Intel and AOL are now discussing a merger which would make them the largest Internet company and in an effort make sure that AOL remains the most widely used program Intel and AOL are running an email beta test When you forward this email to friends Intel can and will track it if you are a Microsoft Windows user for a two week time period For every person that you forward this email to Microsoft will pay you For every person that you sent it to that forwards it on Microsoft will pay you and for every third person that receives it you will be paid Within two weeks Intel will contact you for your address and then send you a check I thought this was a scam myself but a friend of my good friends Aunt Patricia who works at Intel actually got a check for by forwarding this email Try it what have you got to lose Melissa J Haahr Business Manager Northwood Public School Say Bye to Slow Internet xinboxsignuphtml Get Your Private Free Email RE FootballThe weekend looks good I have to do a little homework Other than that I am ready to go Houston just may kick our ass Your room is available either night GT Original Message From SMTP Sent Thursday September AM To Subject Football GT I am planning on coming in for the game this weekend Not sure if it will be Fri night or Sat morning What does your schedule look like for the weekend

RE WeekendI live off of Mopac near Parmer Lane Take a left on Parmer when traveling N or Mopac and then take a left on Adelphi a right on Wycliff and a right onto Marblehead Marblehead See ya manana GT Original Message From SMTP Sent Friday September AM To Townsend George Subject Weekend GT I am planning on driving in Sat I will probably leave Houston around am Should be in Austin at lunch time I cant remember exactly how to get to your casa Can you drop me some directions again Thanks

RE FootballMOBIL NUMBER Original Message From SMTP Sent Friday September AM To Subject RE Football GT I think I will probably come in tonight since the game is so early Are you guys going to try and buy tickets at the gate for BB Email back with your phone numbers so I can call if anything changes Talk at ya later G

RE Missourinight do you plan on staying GT Original Message From SMTP Sent Monday October PM To Subject Missouri GT How is it going Man was that an asswhipping or what that we took from OU Looks like we salvaged some dignity with the CU game I was planning on coming in for the Missouri game I might have my brother and another friend with me How are you set for space Those guys could crash on the couches if its not a problem with you If it is a problem just let me know and we can make other arrangements Talk at ya later G

Hows it going The horns had a decent season I guess Hey do you know how I can get a hold of Ernie Let me know GT

RE Hey BudWhats going on dude Antigua was awesome I survived it without a problem Heather moving in has been a different story I didnt realize how much stuff you could pack into a one bedroom apartment How is your love life The gal from the wedding was pretty hot Are you still chasing that Lets get together soon Our extra bedroom is nicer now My old bed got tossed in a dumpster It smelled like shit Talk to you later GT Original Message From mailto Sent Monday March PM To Subject Hey Bud How is it going Did you survive the honeymoon

RE WhazzupNonPrivilegedpst G I think Heathers Mom will be at the house next weekend Its Heathers BDay Will another weekend work Sorry you and Barb broke up but se la viHow the hell do you spell that french shit Anyway there are other fish in the sea dude Go for a twenty one year old so I can salivate No Le Hace is scheduled for Aug Mark your calendar GT Original Message From Nemec Gerald mailtoGerald NRONcom Sent Thursday July PM To Subject Whazzup Hey Dude How is it going Was thinking about maybe making a road trip next weekend the big A What do you have going on Might just be myself though Barbara and I had a parting of the ways Relationships seems to give me the panics after a couple of months Right now I am working on recharging the girlfriend pipeline

RENonPrivilegedpst G July is good I am taking the first two weeks off in July so sometime during that time would be good We need to go tubing or something No George Jr for a while We know better than to be in hurry Actually I plan on being the father and grandfather of our kids No incest I just going to be old enought to handle both duties I figure it would save money Good to here your taking your time with Barbara She needs to understand youre not in a hurry for a good reason You know how women are tick tocktick tock Damn the clock pisses me off Did you go to China on purpose or did you miss a connection Sounds cool We thought we had historic crap Lets get together dude GT Original Message From mailto Sent Thursday June PM To Subject RE GT Hey guy I am doing good The casa made it through the floods with no problem I was actually out of the country when all that occurred I just got back from two weeks in China Very interesting Saw the Great Wall and a whole lot of other things I am still seeing Barbara the girl I took to your wedding Things are going okay with that I am not very good at the relationship thing right now and she gets frustrated with me Hows the married life Thought there might be a George Jr on the way by now Yes I need to make a trip to Austin soon The next couple of weekends are swamped but maybe sometime in mid to late July What does your Calender look like then G Original Message From Townsend George ENRON mailtoIMCEANOTESTownsendCGeorgeCgtownsendmanorisdEne tE NRONcom Sent Thursday June PM To gerald nemec Email Subject G Whats new dude I havent heard from you so I thought Id bug ya Hows the casalovelife going Did you get some water in the casa You need to come to Austin with your clubs or swimming trunks We could rent a ski boat or something Hope youre doing well George T
